data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER/BRING ALL OFFERS! Situated adjacent to a greenbelt within the guard-gated April Sound, lies your new home! The home boasts lofty ceilings, an abundance of natural light, & modern updates throughout. The layout of the floorplan caters perfectly for hosting & entertaining. The kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances, a sizable island, & overlooks a cozy living space. A loft area presents limitless possibilities, while the primary suite has been lavishly appointed with a fully updated spa-inspired bathroom featuring a deep soaking tub & dual-headed walk-in shower. The generously sized secondary bedrooms are conveniently situated near a beautifully updated bathroom. Seamlessly integrate outdoor living by enjoying the welcoming front deck & the covered back patio. Immerse yourself in the Country Club experience with swift access to the golf club, tennis facilities, pools, marina, & dining options. Ample storage space is provided by the 3-car garage.
